code: @Override public BooleanType getRandom(Random rnd) {     return new BooleanType(rnd.nextBoolean()). }
@Override public void write(DataOutputView out) throws IOException {     out.writeBoolean(this.value). }
@Override public void read(DataInputView in) throws IOException {     this.value = in.readBoolean(). }

@Override public boolean equals(Object obj) {     if (obj instanceof BooleanType) {         BooleanType other = (BooleanType) obj.         return this.value == other.value.     } else {         return false.     } }
